longBusinessSummary: Banco Alfa de Investimento S.A. provides private banking, wealth management, and advisory services in Brazil. It offers financial services, including personal credit and overdraft facilities, vehicle financing, aircraft financing, leasing, working capital, capital market, and payroll loan services, as well as FINAME, FINEM, BNDES automatic, and EXIM services, and financing facilities for importing equipment. Banco Alfa de investimento S.A. was founded in 1925 and is headquartered in São Paulo, Brazil.
